I will give you an example on how to configure taglist

1, If neither .vim nor vimfiles folder exit, you need create it yourself.

2, cp doc/taglist.txt ~/.vim/doc or ~/vimfiles/doc

3, cp plugin/taglist.vim ~/.vim/plugin/ or ~/vimfiles/plugin/

4, :Using Tlist command in vim for testing taglist

5, :Using help taglist command in vim for testing taglist help
